CREATE TABLE [dbo].[FaresData_Fast]
( 
	[id] int ,
	[medallion] [varchar](255)  NULL,
	[hack_license] [varchar](255)  NULL,
	[vendor_id] [varchar](255)  NULL,
	[pickup_datetime] [varchar](255)  NULL,
	[payment_type] [varchar](255)  NULL,
	[fare_amount] [varchar](255)  NULL,
	[surcharge] [varchar](255)  NULL,
	[mta_tax] [varchar](255)  NULL,
	[tip_amount] [varchar](255)  NULL,
	[tolls_amount] [varchar](255)  NULL,
	[total_amount] [varchar](255)  NULL
)
WITH
(
	DISTRIBUTION = HASH ([id]),
	CLUSTERED COLUMNSTORE INDEX
)
GO
